repoman (0.2.1-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Rename app ID to net.tecktron.repoman (owned domain, no github dependency).
  * Change in-app help URL to repoman.tecktron.net (stable owned subdomain).
  * Restore wizard: Existing vs Adding redesign; matched repos with current suite
    skip network checks and only sync enabled state.
  * Info popovers and tooltips on compat checker suite-agnostic and non-PPA rows.
  * Fix availability icon (tecktron-repoman-available, was pamac-tray-no-update).
  * Fix: entry_to_repository normalises .list source paths to .sources.
  * Fix: _show_missing_repos_dialog guards against empty missing list.

